text: Mullsjö AIS is a floorball club in Mullsjö in Sweden. It was established on 1 November 1989 by a group from the Mullsjö Mission Covenant Church. On 2 March 2008, the men's team qualified for the Swedish top division. ==References== ==Other websites== *Official website Category:1989 establishments in Sweden Category:Mullsjö Category:Floorball clubs in Sweden
